Before compiling Astroberry PiFace:

1) libmcp23s17
# git clone https://github.com/piface/libmcp23s17.git
# cd libmcp23s17
# make
# make install

2) libpifacecad
# git clone https://github.com/piface/libpifacecad.git
# cd libpifacecad
# make
# make install

3) libindi-dev
# sudo apt-get install libindi-dev

Compile Astroberry PiFace:
# git clone https://github.com/rkaczorek/astroberry-piface.git
# cd astroberry-piface
# mkdir build
# cd build
# cmake ..
# make
# make install

DONE
